"""
Tool Configuration for TuringMind MCP Server

This module defines which tool groups are enabled/disabled.
Modify ENABLED_TOOL_GROUPS to control which tools are exposed.

Tool Groups:
- login: Authentication flow (initiate_login, poll_login)
- auth: Auth validation (validate_auth)
- code_review: Code review tools (upload_review, get_context, submit_feedback, enable_auto_review)
- code_index: Code indexing (index_codebase, get_related_code, get_project_structure)
- memory: Memory graph (list_memory, get_memory, save_memory, delete_memory, detect_conflicts, resolve_conflict, simulate_impact, explain_decision, get_memory_stats)
- tdd_workflow: TDD/SDD workflow (create_edit_plan, generate_spec, define_required_tests, validate_tests_written, request_code_edit, mark_test_written, validate_tests_passing, complete_tdd_cycle, get_tdd_status, get_audit_trail, get_kanban_data)
- auto_plan: Continuous SDD (analyze_diff, store_auto_plan, get_auto_plans, bundle_plans_for_commit)
- edit_tools: Edit with reasoning (apply_edit, log_reasoning, get_edit_reasoning)
- chat_analysis: Chat analysis (store_chat_analysis_plan, get_chat_analysis_plans, enhance_chat_analysis)
- decisions: Human-in-the-loop decision queue (create_decision, get_pending_decisions, resolve_decision, get_decision_stats)
- issues: Work management (create_issue, get_issue, list_issues, update_issue, create_comment, list_comments) - Linear-compatible naming
- goals: Strategic goals/OKRs (create_goal, get_goal, list_goals, update_goal)
- initiatives: Strategic initiatives (create_initiative, get_initiative, list_initiatives, update_initiative)
- features: Feature management (create_feature, get_feature, list_features, update_feature)
- specs: Strategic specs/requirements (create_strategic_spec, get_strategic_spec, list_strategic_specs, update_strategic_spec)
- risks: Strategic risks (create_strategic_risk, get_strategic_risk, list_strategic_risks, update_strategic_risk)
"""

